headline: Endorsement of Congressman Frank Lucas
body_text: Congressman Frank Lucas is a strong advocate for the people of Oklahomaâ€™s 3rd Congressional District. Frank is working hard to Grow our Economy, Encourage Innovation, Promote American Farmers, Defend the Second Amendment, and Support our Military and Vets. In 2016 and 2020, I won 77 of 77 counties in the Great State of Oklahoma, and I was proud to campaign alongside Oklahoma leaders like Frank. Frank Lucas has my Complete and Total Endorsement!
